    "name": "Navya Renduchintala",
    "rating": 5,
    "text": "Mahatma Gandhi Institute of Technology (MGIT) offers an exceptionally positive academic environment supported by a professional and collaborative working culture. The faculty members are highly committed to maintaining academic excellence and are consistently approachable, ensuring that students receive the necessary guidance and support throughout their learning journey.\n\nOne of the distinguishing strengths of MGIT is its focus on the holistic development of students. In addition to strong academics, the institution actively encourages participation in a wide range of extracurricular activities, including technical clubs, cultural events, and sports. These initiatives provide students with valuable opportunities to enhance their communication, leadership, and teamwork skills, contributing meaningfully to their overall growth."
